      • getMacros

        public java.util.Map<java.lang.String,LatexMacro> getMacros()
        returns the map of macros defined and available to this object PomParser. Each map entry is a pair of a macro name (and LaTeX command String) as a key, and a LatexMacro object (as the value) which models the macro definition.
        Returns:
        the map of macros defined and available to this object PomParser.
